spanGrp.span: ‘A dog was going in a car when a duck appeared before him and he just got that one;
(_) Chichi damĩu karro nã mãĩ pato desãu í wömĩ jeme jebö gugá-wã-ite
he kicked it; it ended up at a sheep’s feet.
(_) je të í tiá-nẽ je mẽnẽu janã' obeja klö mẽ
They took it to play with; they kicked it
Je je jie-wa (_) të í gugá-wã jinõ… jinõ-glö Je tie-gẽ jie-wa të í klö wa
and then one of the kicked it real hard, so hard that it broke the window of the dog’s house.
jeme e-gla të í juã'mẽnẽwãu-mĩ të je chichi jũ bidrio kwã' mẽnẽwãu-mĩ
They ordered to go and get it [the ball];
the duck took it; it went directly into his belly.’
Jie-wa të í juã'u-mĩ je pato të í gugá-wã (_) kawã'u í ñãwa nã
